1 SUMMARY
22 The funds provided by this bond issue, in the amount of $13,485,000, will be used to
33 improve emergency aviation infrastructure, including hospital helipads, fuel systems,
44 automated weather observation systems, communications systems and emergency
55 transport, to improve the safety of and access to critical emergency medical services.
